dct_description_sm: reverendo et illustidno Guilielmo Grimbergio, antverpiensi praesuli dignissimo ; Abrah. Ortelius obsequij deuotionisqe ergo dedicab. consecrabatqe.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, places of historical interest.
Features 3 decorative cartouches and descriptive text.
Inset map: Domini est terra et plenitudo orbis terrarum et universi qui habitant in eo. Psal. 24.
